title: Combat Mission Shock Force FULL (RUS)
description:
This is a Combat Mission Shock Force release from 1C/Snowball that includes

1. Base game
2. Marines expansion
3. British Forces expansion
4. NATO expansion

And patched up to the latest version - 1.32

Alas it is only in russian (text-only translation) but it should be possible to make it english with the help of language archives from the respective version.

Content from the Bonus folder is missing because it's just ads - to make the ISO image smaller.
